   STANHOME Inc. (Westfield, Mass.) -- Alejandro Diaz,
45-year-old president of this direct marketer of
personal-care and home products, was named to the additional
post of chief executive officer, effective next Wednesday,
succeeding H.L. Tower, 58, who will remain chairman. Mr.
Diaz's other current title of chief operating will be
dropped.
