</IN>
<LP>
   LONDON -- Rolls-Royce PLC, Aeritalia and a unit of Alfa
Romeo S.p.A. have agreed to jointly manufacture castings for
gas turbine engines in Italy, the companies said.
   The three will hold equal shares in the joint venture, to
be known as Europea Microfusioni Spaziali, which is to build
