</SO>
<CO>
   RHH
</CO>
<LP>
   H.H. Robertson Co. said it will change its name to
Robertson-Ceco Corp. following the proposed acquisition of
Ceco Industries Inc., Oakbrook Terrace, Ill.
   Headquarters will remain in Pittsburgh, Robertson said.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Robertson has agreed to pay $15 million plus 3.4 million
to 4.1 million of its common shares for Ceco, and to assume
$85 million of Ceco debt.
   Robertson is a building-products concern. Ceco
manufactures doors, metal buildings and roofing systems, and
it provides concrete-forming services.
